      <div class="productText fullRight">
        <h2>Well Connected</h2>
        <p><!-- DO NOT use class 'white-dotted-tab-n-desk' or 'white-dotted-allstops' for links -->
          The Drafting Multitouch Table comes complete with Ethernet, Wi-Fi, and Bluetooth connectivity. It also has an HDMI input and microphone/headphone output via a &#8539;&Prime; mini jack. There is direct access via lockable USB ports. Each Drating Table comes with optional WiDi for wireless screen access. You can also order the optional RFID to extend the unit capabilities.
        </p>
      </div>
