      <h1>Key Features</h1>
    </section>
    
    <ul
      class="slider platform-drafting"
      ng-init="clientSliderIndex = 0"
      rn-carousel
      rn-carousel-control
      rn-carousel-indicator
      rn-carousel-width="responsiveTwoUp()"
      rn-carousel-index="clientSliderIndex"
    >
      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/armed.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Armed &amp; Hyperthready</h3>
        <p>
          The integrated computer is a powerhouse. It includes an Intel® Quad Core i7 4790s&reg; (3.1GHz) with Hyperthreading&reg;, 8MB cache computer with 8 GB of RAM, and a 500GB HDD.
        </p>
      </li>
      
      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/reach.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Reach Out &amp; Touch Everything</h3>
        <p>
          Along with 50+ touch points, the touch surface on the Drafting Tables has palm rejection, a bright HD or 4K / UHD resolution screen (available on the 55 &amp; 65 table) and up to a 60hz refresh rate.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/widi.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>WiDi Ready</h3>
        <p>
          Use the integrated Intel Wireless Display (WiDi) to share your touch table content on any HDMI compatible display. Expand collaborative work options and presentations by using the touch table and an HD screen to include more participants. A WiDi receiver is available as an optional upgrade.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/demanding.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Built for Demanding Spaces</h3>
        <p>
          The Drafting Tables have a chemically strengthened glass top and the chassis is made out of aircraft-grade aluminum and cold-rolled steel. We are proud to say that the Drafting Tables have exceptional build-quality and are perfect for public spaces and other demanding environments. The multitouch Drafting Tables can travel too. They can fit through standard doorways even when packed in a protective ATA case (upgrade option).
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/windows.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Windows 8 &amp; Beyond</h3>
        <p>
          The Drafting Table ships with either Windows 8 64-bit Professional (46) or Windows 7 Professional 64-bit (55 and 65) installed. Thousands of touch-enabled apps for Windows 8 and 7 are now available, and there is even a Windows 7 / 8 dual boot system upgrade option.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/gestureworks.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Creation by Intelligent Design</h3>
        <p>
          The Drafting Tables come with a lifetime license for GestureWorks Core (C++, C# / .NET, Java, Python, and HTML5 / JavaScript) and Open Exhibits (ActionScript). The license includes ticketed, timely support and free upgrades for life. GestureWorks Gameplay is also included: an innovative Windows 8 utility that lets you configure touch, motion and voice controls for your favorite PC games or applications.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/graphically.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>On the Road</h3>
        <p>
          The Drafting Multitouch Table is ruggedized and easy to set up making it perfect for tradeshows, traveling exhibits and special events. You can purchase the table with an optional ATA flight case. You can also rent the Drafting Table 46 and Drafting Table 55 models directly from Ideum.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/warranty.svg' %}
        </div>
